# Per-machine skill installs (Anthropic Skills SDK · `npx skills add ...`)
# These are runtime-loaded into Claude Code from ~/.claude/skills/ via
# symlinks; the per-project `.claude/skills/` and `.agents/skills/` trees
# are reproducible by re-running the install command, so they don't
# belong in version control.
.claude/skills/
.agents/skills/
skills-lock.json

